name: Mars - Ad astra abyssosque
description: We're currently living in a great time of discoveries which "Ad astra abyssoque" translates to "to the depths of the stars" Or put in other way 'to infinity and beyond' we as humankind goind further and further exploring new worlds in the macro or micro cosmos. Or in every aspects of our lives. Ad astra abisosque also invites us to conquer and go as far as to rech the stars but also be able to go as deep to conquer our own depths.
